All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
The App class serves as the entry point for the Minesweeper application.
Cell
The Cell class represents a single cell in the Minesweeper game grid.
CellButton
The CellButton class represents a button in the Minesweeper game grid.
Game
The Game class represents the Minesweeper game logic.
GameController
The GameController class manages the game logic and user interactions for the Minesweeper game.
GameFrame
The GameFrame class represents the main window of the Minesweeper game.
GameMode
Represents the difficulty levels for the Minesweeper game.
GameOverFrame
The GameOverFrame class represents a JFrame that displays a "Game Over!"
GamePanel
The GamePanel class represents the panel where the Minesweeper game grid is displayed.
MainMenu
The MainMenu class represents the main menu of the Minesweeper game.
Player
The Player class represents a player in the Minesweeper game who uses constraint satisfaction to solve the game.
